!snippet perry {{combat().get_combatant(name).add_effect("Agile Perry", "-ac +2", 1, desc="You gain a +2 bonus to AC until the start of your next turn, while the weapon is in your hand and you aren't incapacitated.")}}
-f "Agile Perry | If you make an unarmed strike as part of the Attack action on your turn and are holding a kensei weapon, you can use it to defend yourself if it is a melee weapon. You gain a +2 bonus to AC until the start of your next turn, while the weapon is in your hand and you aren't incapacitated."